    "body": "1. Delete everything from inside /tmp/<user>/spack-stage\r\n2. Execute \"spack stage <package with resources>\"\r\n3. Confirm presence of package and resource directories in staging directory.\r\n4. Execute \"spack clean --stage\"\r\n5. Verify that package staging directory is removed, but resource directories remain.\r\n6. Execute \"spack clean --all\"\r\n7. Verify that resource directories still remain in staging directory.\r\n\r\nUsing spack v0.15.4 on a RHEL7 machine.\r\n",
